OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FThe first of 62 inquests of patients
OL,8,Ftreated by rogue breast surgeon Ian
OL,9,FPaterson begins today as the disgraced
OL,10,Fdoctor has been told by a coroner he
OL,11,Fmust give evidence.
OL,13,FThe first of the inquests, which are
OL,14,Fexpected to be heard over a period of
OL,15,Fat least eight months at Birmingham
OL,16,Fand Solihull Coroners Court, will
OL,17,Ftouch upon the death of 43-year-old
OL,18,FChloe Nikitas, an environmental
OL,19,Fconsultant from Tamworth who died at
OL,20,Fthe Priory Hospital in Birmingham on
OL,21,FApril 13 2008.
