OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon must give
OL,4,Cevidence at inquests of 62 of his
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FThe 66-year-old, who is serving a 20-
OL,8,Fyear custodial term after being
OL,9,Fconvicted of multiple counts of
OL,10,Fwounding in 2017, was accused of
OL,11,Fattempting to delay the hearings after
OL,12,Flodging an application to have his
OL,13,Fwitness summons revoked the day before
OL,14,Fthe first inquest was due to start on
OL,15,FOctober 10.
