OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon must give
OL,4,Cevidence at inquests of 62 of his
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FPaterson's lawyer argued that health
OL,8,Fconcerns, a lack of legal
OL,9,Frepresentation and "inadequate
OL,10,Ffacilities to prepare" meant his
OL,11,Fwitness summons for the judge-led
OL,12,Finquests should be withdrawn.
OL,14,FIn a ruling published on Monday,
OL,15,FCoroner Richard Foster said he could
OL,16,F"find no reason" that Paterson could
OL,17,Fnot give evidence remotely at the
OL,18,Finquests, the first of which is due to
OL,19,Fstart today.
