OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon must give
OL,4,Cevidence at inquests of 62 of his
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FHe said: "It is perfectly reasonable
OL,8,Fin all the circumstances to require
OL,9,Fhim to do so, taking into account the
OL,10,Fpublic interest and the importance of
OL,11,Fhis participation to my investigations
OL,12,Fand these inquests.
OL,14,F"I can and will make all necessary
OL,15,Fadaptations to the court process to
OL,16,Fachieve the best evidence from Mr
OL,17,FPaterson."
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@AOUyD@JO]
