OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon must give
OL,4,Cevidence at inquests of 62 of his
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FThe court heard claims from Paterson's
OL,8,Flegal team last week that the jailed
OL,9,Fdoctor, originally from Glasgow, would
OL,10,Fstruggle to remain focused during the
OL,11,Finquests and process large volumes of
OL,12,Fpaperwork due to health issues.
OL,14,FJudge Foster said he would make
OL,15,F"appropriate measures and adjustments"
OL,16,Fto make sure Paterson could take part
OL,17,Fin the proceedings, including regular
OL,18,Frest breaks, adding: "His evidence
OL,19,Fwill be of the utmost assistance and
OL,20,Fany evidence is better than none.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@fO]zD@VOU
