OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon must give
OL,4,Cevidence at inquests of 62 of his
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FPaterson, who was living in Altrincham
OL,8,Fin Greater Manchester when he was
OL,9,Ftried and convicted, was found to have
OL,10,Fcarried out unnecessary and unapproved
OL,11,Fprocedures on more than 1,000 breast
OL,12,Fcancer patients over 14 years.
OL,14,FThe consultant breast surgeon was
OL,15,Femployed by the Heart of England NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust and practised in the
OL,17,Findependent sector at Spire Parkway
OL,18,Fand Spire Little Aston, all in
OL,19,FBirmingham between 1997 and 2011.
