OL,3,CDisgraced breast surgeon must give
OL,4,Cevidence at inquests of 62 of his
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FHe carried out "cleavage-sparing"
OL,8,Fmastectomies on patients, which left
OL,9,Fbehind breast tissue and risked a
OL,10,Freturn of cancer.
OL,12,FAn independent inquiry ruled that he
OL,13,Fhad carried out hundreds of
OL,14,Funnecessary operations on hundreds of
OL,15,Fpatients, exaggerating or inventing
OL,16,Fcancer risks.
